5
00:00:16,600 --> 00:00:19,520
What?

6
00:00:19,520 --> 00:00:22,540
Clear off your desks.

7
00:00:31,680 --> 00:00:34,330
Akkun. Akkun!

8
00:00:34,330 --> 00:00:36,130
Let me borrow your eraser.

9
00:00:38,260 --> 00:00:39,640
No!

10
00:00:39,640 --> 00:00:41,890
- So unkind.
- I only have one.

11
00:00:41,890 --> 00:00:44,740
- Then split it in half.
- No way!

12
00:00:44,740 --> 00:00:46,380
Are you leaving me to fail?

13
00:00:46,380 --> 00:00:48,430
