16
00:00:52,430 --> 00:00:53,650
- Stop it.
- Hand it over.

17
00:00:53,650 --> 00:00:56,190
- Nope!
- Aoki.

18
00:00:59,120 --> 00:01:00,890
Use this.

19
00:01:02,130 --> 00:01:04,560
