35
00:02:10,640 --> 00:02:12,910
[Ida♡]

36
00:02:15,490 --> 00:02:17,260
Was that a...

37
00:02:17,880 --> 00:02:21,410
"love charm," that is popular among girls?

38
00:02:23,840 --> 00:02:29,300
Which means, is the person Hashimoto likes...
[Ida♡]

39
00:02:30,770 --> 00:02:33,090
Ida?

40
00:02:33,090 --> 00:02:35,060
I see.

41
00:02:35,060 --> 00:02:40,020
You're so modest, Hashimoto.

42
00:02:40,020 --> 00:02:42,880
I liked that part of you, too.

43
00:02:42,880 --> 00:02:47,880
We'll begin at the half-hour mark. Be sure to focus.

44
00:02:52,700 --> 00:02:55,480
