60
00:04:15,920 --> 00:04:19,320
So the "heart" means... Seriously?

61
00:04:19,320 --> 00:04:23,500
Since when? Why me? To be honest, we're not even that close.

62
00:04:23,500 --> 00:04:27,730
We only spoke... the other day...

63
00:04:27,730 --> 00:04:30,890
Hey, Ida, your button is hanging loose.

64
00:04:32,090 --> 00:04:33,510
Oh, thanks.

65
00:04:33,510 --> 00:04:35,240
