66
00:04:35,240 --> 00:04:38,290
I'll help you. Give me half.

67
00:04:38,290 --> 00:04:39,710
Thanks.

68
00:04:39,710 --> 00:04:41,480
And before that...

69
00:04:43,350 --> 00:04:45,250
Didn't you bring your umbrella?

70
00:04:45,880 --> 00:04:48,240
I'll walk you halfway.

71
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:49,900
Thank you.

72
00:04:54,700 --> 00:04:57,700
We actually had a good thing going on!

73
00:04:59,900 --> 00:05:01,490
Ida.

74
00:05:01,490 --> 00:05:02,970
What it is?

75
00:05:06,110 --> 00:05:07,720
So...

76
00:05:09,220 --> 00:05:11,910
how did the quiz go?

77
00:05:11,910 --> 00:05:14,360
