78
00:05:15,750 --> 00:05:17,300
I see.

79
00:05:21,420 --> 00:05:25,460
Are you free after school?

80
00:05:25,460 --> 00:05:28,060
I want to tell you something regarding that eraser.

81
00:05:29,930 --> 00:05:31,900
Can't you do it now?

82
00:05:31,900 --> 00:05:36,220
Not now. It would be bad if others overheard us.

83
00:05:36,220 --> 00:05:38,120
See you on the rooftop after school.

84
00:05:48,100 --> 00:05:50,090
- Aren't you hungry?
- I am.

85
00:05:50,090 --> 00:05:52,940
- I only have candies.
- Can I have one?

86
00:05:54,900 --> 00:05:58,920
Dammit, he's definitely got the wrong idea.

87
00:05:58,920 --> 00:06:00,870
I should tell him the truth.

88
00:06:00,870 --> 00:06:06,190
Aoki, can I have my eraser back?

89
00:06:06,190 --> 00:06:07,680
Oh, sorry.

90
00:06:08,740 --> 00:06:10,110
Here you go.

91
00:06:10,110 --> 00:06:12,720
You really saved me. Thanks.

92
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:14,290
No worries.

93
00:06:17,770 --> 00:06:19,250
What's wrong?

94
00:06:19,250 --> 00:06:21,090
Aoki...

95
00:06:22,400 --> 00:06:24,740
perhaps...

96
00:06:26,320 --> 00:06:28,530
did you see it?

97
00:06:28,530 --> 00:06:31,900
- What?
- So you did.

98
00:06:33,050 --> 00:06:36,860
- Sorry.
- Don't be sorry.

99
00:06:36,860 --> 00:06:39,450
- I should thank you instead.
- Pardon?

100
00:06:40,410 --> 00:06:45,390
