101
00:06:45,390 --> 00:06:47,510
There's no way I would do that.

102
00:06:47,530 --> 00:06:50,390
Thank you for keeping it a secret.

103
00:06:54,940 --> 00:06:57,740
Hashimoto, aren't you going to go for it?

104
00:06:57,740 --> 00:06:58,970
What?

105
00:06:58,970 --> 00:07:00,790
A confession.

106
00:07:00,790 --> 00:07:04,540
Me? No, there is no way I can.

107
00:07:04,540 --> 00:07:07,050
