00:18:09,310 --> 00:18:14,230
♫ I want to tell someone, but I can't. Yes, the secret touch... ♫

253
00:18:14,230 --> 00:18:19,660
If only I had my eraser, it wouldn't have turned out this way.

254
00:18:20,390 --> 00:18:25,390
♫ So I hid it in passing rain ♫

255
00:18:25,390 --> 00:18:31,540
♫ While I feel my frustration for the first time ♫

256
00:18:35,450 --> 00:18:38,530
Aoki, don't be stupid.

257
00:18:39,800 --> 00:18:44,480
You damn fool! I know you have a broken heart, but don't die.

258
00:18:46,630 --> 00:18:48,460
Excuse me?

259
00:18:48,460 --> 00:18:51,200
Ouch. Get off of me.

260
00:18:52,540 --> 00:18:56,440
